OL,7,FTo mark the 100th anniversary of her
OL,8,Felection, Marie Randall's family have
OL,9,Fbeen sharing their memories of her.
OL,11,FJenny Jee is the great niece of Marie
OL,12,FRandall, and has traced her lineage
OL,13,Fback to Marie via her grandfather,
OL,14,FLieutenant Colonel Robert Randall, who
OL,15,Fwas Marie's brother.
OL,17,F"We loved her. But not everyone in the
OL,18,Ffamily did, they were scared of her."
