OL,7,FJenny Jee's son Nic, says the family
OL,8,Fcalled Marie 'Aunty Totty', "I don't
OL,9,Fthink we could pronounce (Marie) so we
OL,10,Fcalled her Aunty Totty".
OL,12,FWoman in Public Life nominated Marie
OL,13,Ffor a Blue Plaque which is being
OL,14,Funveiled by Deputy Bailiff, Jessica
OL,15,FRoland, at the Deputy's childhood
OL,16,Fhome, One St Julian's.
