OL,7,FThe plaque is the second to
OL,8,Fcommemorate a woman in Guernsey, the
OL,9,Ffirst plaque was for Marie Ozanne who
OL,10,Fspoke up against the naziand there are
OL,11,Fcurrently 11 honouring men.
OL,13,FThe plaque has been funded by Women in
OL,14,FPublic Life, along with Marie's family
OL,15,Fand donations from islanders.
