OL,3,C'We loved her': 100 years since
OL,4,CGuernsey's first female deputy was
OL,5,Celected
OL,7,FIslanders in Guernsey who helped fund
OL,8,Fthe plaque have been able to add a
OL,9,Fpersonal dedication.
OL,11,FOne islander said: "The year Marie was
OL,12,Felected, a ground-breaking moment in
OL,13,FGuernsey politics. Guernsey women,
OL,14,Fover 30, had only secured the right to
OL,15,Fvote 4 years earlier so she was a
OL,16,Fremarkable pioneer."
OL,18,FAnother said: "As a tribute to my Mum
OL,19,Fwho has campaigned for women's rights
OL,20,Fin her way and for my Dad who has
OL,21,Fsupported her."
